*******-_________________
type 
SPARK_HOME=/opt/spark/bin
PATH="user/local/$bin:...................local/games:$SPARK_HOME/bin"
cd /opt/spark/sbin
ls
*****-----
u will see files like master.sh,slave sh.
to start master type
sbin$./start-master.sh
copy the url given and paste in browser

to run slave type
root:/opt/spark/sbin$./start-slave.sh

to go to scala terminal
$opt/spark
ls
